<p><span class="lede"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-77031" src="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-3-745x497.jpg" alt="2024 Ducati Multistrada V4 RS" width="745" height="497" srcset="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-3-745x497.jpg 745w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-3-420x280.jpg 420w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-3-180x120.jpg 180w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-3-570x380.jpg 570w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-3-135x90.jpg 135w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-3-1200x801.jpg 1200w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-3-258x172.jpg 258w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-3-360x240.jpg 360w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-3-720x480.jpg 720w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-3-275x183.jpg 275w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-3-150x100.jpg 150w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-3.jpg 1490w" sizes="(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px" /><br />
‘Choose it all,’</span> Ducati boasts about the 2024 <a href="https://www.ducati.com/us/en/bikes/multistrada/multistrada-v4-rs">Multistrada V4 RS</a> model, but keen eyes will note the forged 17-inch alloys, Pirelli Corsa rubber and sportier ergonomics as a diversion from the model’s ‘many roads’ roots. Like the current Pike’s Peak Multi, it’s a mix of pavement prowess and touring ability that inspires the Multistrada V4 RS, taken to all-new heights with the 180 hp Desmosedici engine from Panigale.<span id="more-77028"></span></p>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-77047" src="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-19-745x497.jpg" alt="2024 Ducati Multistrada V4 RS" width="745" height="497" srcset="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-19-745x497.jpg 745w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-19-420x280.jpg 420w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-19-180x120.jpg 180w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-19-768x512.jpg 768w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-19-570x380.jpg 570w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-19-135x90.jpg 135w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-19-1200x801.jpg 1200w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-19-258x172.jpg 258w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-19-360x240.jpg 360w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-19-720x480.jpg 720w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-19-275x183.jpg 275w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-19-150x100.jpg 150w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-19.jpg 1490w" sizes="(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px" /><br />
The hyper-adventure segment is heating up for 2024, and Ducati’s V4 RS isn’t holding any punches. In place of the standard 170 hp V4 Granturismo mill, this exclusive RS Multi makes use of Ducati’s Moto-GP-derived 1,103 cc Desmosedici Stradale engine. Good for 180 hp with Euro 5+ homologation, the Desmo V4 has been tuned for aggressive, but usable acceleration on the street and limited to 13,500 rpm.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-77029" src="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-1-745x497.jpg" alt="Ducati Multistrada V4 RS Dry Clutch" width="745" height="497" srcset="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-1-745x497.jpg 745w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-1-420x280.jpg 420w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-1-180x120.jpg 180w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-1-570x380.jpg 570w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-1-135x90.jpg 135w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-1-1200x801.jpg 1200w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-1-258x172.jpg 258w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-1-360x240.jpg 360w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-1-720x480.jpg 720w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-1-275x183.jpg 275w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-1-150x100.jpg 150w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-1.jpg 1490w" sizes="(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px" /><br />
But don’t think for a second that they’ve hamstrung it, though, as many go-fast goodies from the <a href="https://www.bikeexif.com/future-classics-2023">Panigale</a> and Streetfighter models are found on the V4 RS. The sportier air filter system comes straight from the SP2 Panigale, as does the billet aluminum dry clutch assembly and quick shifter. Rounding out the installation is a specially designed exhaust system with an Akrapovič silencer, promising a near superbike soundtrack at high rpm.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-77040" src="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-12-745x745.jpg" alt="Ducati Multistrada V4 RS" width="745" height="745" srcset="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-12-745x745.jpg 745w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-12-420x420.jpg 420w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-12-768x768.jpg 768w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-12-380x380.jpg 380w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-12-90x90.jpg 90w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-12-1200x1200.jpg 1200w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-12-360x360.jpg 360w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-12-720x720.jpg 720w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-12-275x275.jpg 275w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-12-150x150.jpg 150w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-12.jpg 1490w" sizes="(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px" /><br />
The Desmo engine serves as a stressed member in the chassis, and Ducati has gone to great lengths to lighten and upgrade the platform for more aggressive riding. The new aluminum monocoque frame features a more sporty 25.75-degree steering head and a new titanium subframe. While we&#8217;re still waiting on final figures, weight savings in the chassis and mechanicals are rumored to be nearly 20 pounds.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-77035" src="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-7-745x497.jpg" alt="Riding the Ducati Multistrada V4 RS" width="745" height="497" srcset="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-7-745x497.jpg 745w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-7-420x280.jpg 420w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-7-180x120.jpg 180w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-7-768x512.jpg 768w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-7-570x380.jpg 570w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-7-135x90.jpg 135w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-7-1200x801.jpg 1200w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-7-258x172.jpg 258w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-7-360x240.jpg 360w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-7-720x480.jpg 720w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-7-275x183.jpg 275w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-7-150x100.jpg 150w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-7.jpg 1490w" sizes="(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px" /><br />
Like the Pike’s Peak model, the V4 RS wears Marchesini 17-inch forged aluminum wheels on both ends, shod in Pirelli Diablo Rosso IV Corsa tires. Ducati has also moved the pegs higher and further back to improve lean angle, and the handlebar is now rigidly fixed to the triple clamp for a sharper feel.</p>
<p>Suspension is trick on the V4 RS as well, consisting of fully adjustable Öhlins Smart EC 2.0 event-based hardware, which automatically adjusts to your riding style. Twin Brembo Stylema 4-piston calipers clamp down on 330 mm radial discs up front, and Bosch-Brembo corning ABS keeps the whole system in check.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-77030" src="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-2-745x497.jpg" alt="Ducati V4 RS Livery " width="745" height="497" srcset="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-2-745x497.jpg 745w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-2-420x280.jpg 420w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-2-180x120.jpg 180w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-2-570x380.jpg 570w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-2-135x90.jpg 135w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-2-1200x801.jpg 1200w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-2-258x172.jpg 258w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-2-360x240.jpg 360w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-2-720x480.jpg 720w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-2-275x183.jpg 275w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-2-150x100.jpg 150w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-2.jpg 1490w" sizes="(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px" /><br />
As you’d expect from a flagship Ducati product, the V4 RS is fit with all the latest tech, including every three-letter acronym imaginable. There’s adaptive cruise, blind-spot detection, traction control, wheelie control and more. Along with all the acronyms, four riding modes and an additional four power modes are accessed through a 6.5-inch color TFT display.</p>
<p>Loaded with top-tier components and the heart of a track star, it comes as no surprise the V4 RS will set you back a whopping $37,995. Chalk it up as the price to pay for having your cake and eating it too, or as Ducati puts it, <em>choosing it all</em>.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-77044" src="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-16-745x497.jpg" alt="Ducati Multistrada V4 RS Wheelie" width="745" height="497" srcset="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-16-745x497.jpg 745w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-16-420x280.jpg 420w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-16-180x120.jpg 180w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-16-768x512.jpg 768w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-16-570x380.jpg 570w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-16-135x90.jpg 135w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-16-1200x801.jpg 1200w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-16-258x172.jpg 258w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-16-360x240.jpg 360w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-16-720x480.jpg 720w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-16-275x183.jpg 275w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-16-150x100.jpg 150w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ducati-multistrada-v4-rs-16.jpg 1490w" sizes="(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px" /></p>
